WEBVTT

00:03:56.840 --> 00:04:05.110
ask for a job, help in exams, success
in love, and some people go there to relax.

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:08.696
For a moment of respite
from the daily grind of life.

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:13.376
As part of my job I have seen many 
shrines, temples and mosques.

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:17.736
What I got is that these are also
horizons of a kind in society

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:20.176
we go to look for ourselves.

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:21.336
Let's move on.

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:23.216
In smaller towns you must have seen

00:04:23.240 --> 00:04:26.536
people sitting at the railway
station without any reason.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:30.776
They have no train
to catch, no one to meet,